description: West Island Brands Inc. engages in the medical marijuana business. It offers IONIC MIST, a spray mist that captures and neutralizes cannabis smoke odors. The company was formerly known as Matica Enterprises Inc. and changed its name to West Island Brands Inc. in October 2021. West Island Brands Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Boris Ivan Ziger HBA, MBA
